{"tid":2498523,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇得多淫片會空虛","createTime":"2021-04-21T08:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:41:30.000Z","uid":373951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"831774644fb6250fec341f3bebfc4062ba4af0ad","tid":2498523,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:29:36.000Z","msg":"覺得叫床聲係假，女優既表情又係假。全部都係假，全部都係雞。幾靚既女神都可以為錢收左錢去拍AV，有時諗到女神咁樣比班柒毒屌都好SAD。睇完AV之後個種空虛感，有時睇得多片真係會麻木。有Join過戒手淫Group，覺得戒唔到就退左。<br />\n<br />\n而家諗緊要唔要將電腦裡面，相澤南個File Del左佢。但係唔捨得Del，會慣左擺係到。就算唔睇其他，都係唔捨得公主殿下。我覺得我對女人幾專一，幾多年都淨係鐘意相澤南一個。人大左，望身體都只係覺得成團肉。乜都覺好空虛，覺唔覺？"},{"pid":"b24a2ea592b4788f001d8bda560a04a2cb51b87e","tid":2498523,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"其實戒得多丁都係會空虛<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUxcw6CkW5vSBoSZsV7hJFPqbgnNGvJJsTmXTFBAxQGS1?filename=vcW1OE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcW1OE1.jpg&h=e7fe9462&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"943f649a832fecbd543ab0089e95b3dd6a287137","tid":2498523,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"1. 你賢者模式緊，聽日就無事<br />\n2. 買Oculus Quest 2睇VR"},{"pid":"8ed3cbb767fe75b0278cb189e0044e9f5c872c76","tid":2498523,"uid":192913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"好想打j呀"},{"pid":"88d5c98de8b88128df6bbfa389e5892de964cc56","tid":2498523,"uid":61853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"睇多次beauty venus 5先"},{"pid":"3888b4e49c138e3a9e671b6c0450a9932d7a70e3","tid":2498523,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T08:36:35.000Z","msg":"放開啲諗，做戲都可以令我睇到射，嚟真我咪精盡人亡？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0eb3fee70192117b800153e2f289825ca8844ed","tid":2498523,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislik